jsx.graphic
Class VML

java.lang.Object
  js.Disposable
      jsx.Configurable
          jsx.graphic.VML

public final class VML
extends Configurable

A utility class providing static methods to create basic VML components.

A VML component wraps a VML element and is Configurable.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org

isStyled

public static final boolean isStyled(Component v)

Is the shape of a VML component specified in the CSS2 properties.

Parameters:
v - The current VML component.
Returns:
true if the shape of the underlying VML element of the current component is also specified in the CSS2 properties. Otherwise, if the shape of the underlying VML element of the current component is only defined by its attributes, this method returns false.
